---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout 
  title="Full Head of Highlights" 
  price="$180" 
  duration="2.5-3 hours"
  image="https://storage.googleapis.com/msgsndr/BLeUCGmXOpptWsB7PyZu/media/67f8d56db95d201419a3c858.png"
>
  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Complete Transformation with Maximum Dimension</h2>
  
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
    Full head highlights deliver the ultimate in hair transformation, creating stunning dimension from root to tip. This comprehensive service covers your entire head, ensuring seamless color distribution and maximum impact. Whether you're going for subtle sun-kissed strands or dramatic contrast, full highlights offer endless possibilities for customization.
  </p>

  <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">The Full Highlight Experience</h3>
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
    Our full head highlight service involves applying foils throughout 100% of your hair, including the underneath sections often missed with partial applications. This creates incredible depth, movement, and light reflection from every angle. The result is hair that looks professionally colored, vibrant, and full of life no matter how you style it.
  </p>

  <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Benefits of Full Head Coverage</h3>
  <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
    <li>Complete, even color distribution throughout</li>
    <li>Maximum dimension and light reflection</li>
    <li>Ability to go significantly lighter overall</li>
    <li>Perfect base for future color changes</li>
    <li>Stunning results from every angle</li>
    <li>Ideal for dramatic transformations</li>
    <li>Can incorporate multiple tones for complexity</li>
    <li>Works beautifully with all styling options</li>
  </ul>

  <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Ideal Candidates</h3>
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
    Full head highlights are perfect for:
  </p>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
    <div class="bg-[#F8F9FA] rounded-lg p-4">
      <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Color Enthusiasts</h4>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Those who love maintaining vibrant, dimensional color</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-[#F8F9FA] rounded-lg p-4">
      <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Major Changes</h4>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Clients wanting to go significantly lighter</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-[#F8F9FA] rounded-lg p-4">
      <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Fine Hair</h4>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Creates illusion of thickness and volume</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-[#F8F9FA] rounded-lg p-4">
      <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Style Variety</h4>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Those who frequently change their hairstyle</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Advanced Techniques</h3>
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
    Melissa employs various advanced highlighting techniques to achieve your desired look:
  </p>
  <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
    <li><strong>Foilyage:</strong> Combines foils with balayage for natural results</li>
    <li><strong>Teasy lights:</strong> Creates softer grow-out lines</li>
    <li><strong>Back-to-back foils:</strong> Maximum lightness and coverage</li>
    <li><strong>Dimensional placement:</strong> Strategic color for movement</li>
    <li><strong>Root smudging:</strong> Seamless blend at the roots</li>
  </ul>

  <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">The Application Process</h3>
  <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
    <li>Thorough consultation and strand test if needed</li>
    <li>Protection of skin and clothing</li>
    <li>Systematic sectioning of entire head</li>
    <li>Custom color formulation for your goals</li>
    <li>Precise foil application throughout</li>
    <li>Monitored processing for optimal lift</li>
    <li>Gentle removal and deep conditioning</li>
    <li>Custom toner application for perfect finish</li>
    <li>Professional styling to showcase results</li>
  </ol>

  <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Investment & Maintenance</h3>
  <div class="bg-[#FFDEE2] bg-opacity-20 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
    <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3">Maintaining Your Investment:</h4>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
      <li>Touch-ups recommended every 6-8 weeks</li>
      <li>Use salon-quality color care products</li>
      <li>Weekly hair masks for hydration</li>
      <li>Purple shampoo 1-2 times per week</li>
      <li>Heat protection essential for styling</li>
      <li>Regular toner refreshes between highlights</li>
      <li>Trimming every 6-8 weeks for healthy ends</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Color Possibilities</h3>
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
    With full head highlights, your color options are virtually limitless. Whether you prefer natural beachy blondes, rich caramels, or fashion-forward platinums, Melissa will create a custom color palette that enhances your skin tone and matches your personality. The comprehensive coverage allows for subtle gradations and multiple tones that create truly unique, personalized results.
  </p>

  <div class="bg-[#D3E4FD] bg-opacity-20 rounded-lg p-6">
    <p class="text-gray-700 italic">
      "Full head highlights are an investment in yourself. The confidence that comes from having beautifully dimensional, professionally colored hair is priceless. It's not just about looking good â€“ it's about feeling amazing every single day."
    </p>
  </div>
</ServiceLayout>